

VimWiki

A VimWiki is a set of files that work as a wiki in Vim.

Add this to your ~/.vimrc

:noremap gf :e <cfile><cr>

Use gf on a word to open up a file with that name.

RecentChanges

Use <CTRL>-o to go back to the previous file.

Use gx on a link to open that link in your browser.

https://google.com

There is no standard format for wiki files other than WikiFormat.

Use the update.sh script to update RecentChanges
